data.title: Who Is The Most Famous August In The World?
data.meta_description: Over 50 fans have voted on the 60+ people on Who Is The Most Famous August In The World?. Current Top 3: Augustus, August Diehl, August Stradal
data.text:
How many celebrities named August can you think of? The famous Augusts below have many different professions, including notable actors named August, famous writers named August, and even musicians named August.

August Wilson is certainly one of the most famous Augusts on this list. One of the famous playwrights named August, he wrote ten plays known as The Century Cycle. He won the Pulitzer Prize for Drama for his plays Fences and The Piano Lesson.

Another of the famous people with the first name August is August Strindberg. He is also a playwright and novelist. The Father, Miss Julie, and Creditors are among his popular works.

Did we forget one of your favorite famous people named August? Just add them to the list!
